                                    <strong>${object.applicant_id.partner_name},</strong>
                                </h5>
                                <p style="color: #676767;line-height: 145%;font-size: 17px;">Welcome to CSM Technologies Pvt. Ltd.</p>
                                <p style="color: #676767;line-height: 145%;font-size: 17px;">${object.otp} is the One Time Password (OTP) for Onboarding process.</p>
                                <p style="color: #676767;line-height: 145%;font-size: 17px;">This OTP is usable only once and is valid for 10 mins.</p>
                                <p style="color: #676767;line-height: 145%;font-size: 17px;">Please do not share the OTP with anyone for security reasons.</p>
                                <br/>
                                <p style="color: #676767;line-height: 145%;font-size: 17px;">
                                    Thanks & regards
                                    <br/>
                                    CSM Technologies Pvt. Ltd.
